Package Maze

Class Wall

java.lang.Object
Maze.CellOLD
Maze.Wall
Direct Known Subclasses:
Logo
public class Wall extends Cell
Cell type that is not able to be passed through, also takes up majority of a Maze as a maze is made up of Walls.
